## Go-Live Criteria
<!-- Specific, measurable conditions that confirm go-live is successful -->
| Criterion | Threshold | Measurement Method |
|-----------|-----------|-------------------|
| Error rate | < {{error_threshold}}% | {{error_measurement}} |
| Latency p99 | < {{latency_threshold}}ms | {{latency_measurement}} |
| Throughput | > {{throughput_threshold}} req/s | {{throughput_measurement}} |
| Smoke tests | 100% pass | {{smoke_measurement}} |

## Rollback Triggers
<!-- Conditions that automatically trigger rollback -->
| Trigger | Threshold | Action |
|---------|-----------|--------|
| Error rate | > {{rb_error_threshold}}% | Immediate rollback |
| P1 incident | Any | Rollback assessment within 15min |
| Latency p99 | > {{rb_latency_threshold}}ms for {{rb_duration}} | Rollback assessment |

